=== 星際飛行 ===
自地球出发，到达火星所需的能量，在各个行星较少，仅次于[[金星|金星]]。利用[[霍曼轉移軌道|霍曼轉移軌道]]到达火星大概需要九个月。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.phy6.org/stargaze/Smars1.htm |title=Flight to Mars: How Long? And along what path? |publisher=Phy6.org |date= |accessdate=2013-08-01 |archive-date=2012-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120913081839/http://www.phy6.org/stargaze/Smars1.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>增加能量、燃油，就能够修改转移轨道，在六到七个月的时间里到达火星。载有无人探测器的火箭就采用了这种方法缩短飛行时间。以目前的科技将飞行时间进一步缩短到六個月以下并不现实，不过，这一目標在未来可借助[[可变比冲磁等离子体火箭|可变比冲磁等离子体火箭]]、[[核热火箭|核热火箭]]等等技术实现。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.techbriefs.com/content/view/1768/32/ |title=NASA Tech Briefs - Variable-Specific-Impulse Magnetoplasma Rocket<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2008-12-19 |archive-date=2008-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081211065353/http://www.techbriefs.com/content/view/1768/32/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>采用前一种技术，四十天内就能达到火星；采用后一种技术，两个星期内就能达到火星。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.newscientist.com/article/dn17476-ion-engine-could-one-day-power-39day-trips-to-mars.html?full=true |title=Ion engine could one day power 39-day trips to Mars |accessdate=2013-09-22 |archive-date=2013-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928174942/http://www.newscientist.com/article/dn17476-ion-engine-could-one-day-power-39day-trips-to-mars.html?full=true |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=autogenerated1>{{Cite book|last=Zubrin|first=Robert|title=The Case for Mars: The Plan to Settle the Red Planet and Why We Must|publisher=Touchstone|year=1996|isbn=0-684-83550-9|pages=}}</ref>缩短飞行时间的另一种方法是采用速度不断加快的推进器，如[[太阳帆|太阳帆]]和[[离子推进器|离子推进器]]。

太空人在飞行期间需要受到保护，因为[[游离辐射|游离辐射]]和[[太阳风|太阳风]]都会损害人体DNA，提高患癌风险。科学家估计，长期进行星际飞行，患癌风险会增加1到19%。男性的患癌风险是3.4%，而女性的患癌风险则更加高，因为女性的腺体组织较为大。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://science.nasa.gov/headlines/y2004/17feb_radiation.htm |title=NASA: Space radiation between Earth and Mars poses a hazard to astronauts. |accessdate=2013-09-22 |archive-date=2010-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100405082513/http://science.nasa.gov/headlines/y2004/17feb_radiation.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

